abstract: British regulators are investigating potential antitrust violations involving an unnamed Procter & Gamble subsidiary, the consumer products company said Thursday in a Securities and Exchange Commission filing.
lead_paragraph: British regulators are investigating potential antitrust violations involving an unnamed Procter & Gamble subsidiary, the consumer products company said Thursday in a Securities and Exchange Commission filing.

headline.main: Procter & Gamble Discloses E.U. Antitrust Probes
